data.text: This Kutjevo Bedding is perfect for adding modern style to any bedroom. Made of 100% cotton, it offers a soft and cozy sleep experience while also being easy to care for with non-chlorine bleach only. This bedding was crafted in India with attention to detail and an eye for style. Give your bedroom the upgrade it deserves with this modern Kutjevo Bedding!
